			<td align="center" valign="middle">
				<a name="p205130"></a>
				<b class="postauthor">Zepper</b>
			</td>
			<td width="100%" height="25">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p205130">Re: MMC3 &quot;when does the irq fire&quot; test rom</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=205130#p205130"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sun Sep 24, 2017 7:59 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
